like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你嗰鄰居個個窮人，全座低質哂</blockquote><br />\n大把公屋富戶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等緊被房署趕走！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買番自己個單位咪得囉，反正咁平</blockquote><br />\n大把精神病人住公屋"},{"pid":"20025554cbf1b979f9fc17b0d44f1a5b2ee126bc","tid":439652,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屋住環境唔係單睇室內<br />\n社區 配套 樓宇問題 治安 衛生...<br />\n全部都影響你生活<br />\n如果你單單覺得閂埋門就得<br />\n其他咩都唔關事<br />\n咁不如訓棺材算啦</blockquote><br />\n所以我咪話質素差啲囉，無話無分別，只係差別唔大</blockquote><br />\n一般而言以上問題私樓無公屋咁嚴重<br />\n當然私樓都有其他問題 (圍標 管理費 etc) <br />\n<br />\n假設私樓公屋呎數一樣又供完<br />\n你揀邊樣?"},{"pid":"78439a3a3fd17da4fcb974247d5e7ebc5bcdd413","tid":439652,"uid":123605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"公屋特別多精神病人 少數族裔<br />\n你唔介意拖條女返屋企不停比人撩/望?<br />\n唔係話私樓無 但一定無公屋咁多問題"},{"pid":"213161e9f6599b164bbe9cfd1f93f2f38b7f5122","tid":439652,"uid":52595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:00:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a081f81ab4f3a6e8a7361217cd06319cccacae3","tid":439652,"uid":32425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"補居屋都唔補公屋！"},{"pid":"c4056cbafbadaed55b5ba20f6f3f6bf3fabe5cc9","tid":439652,"uid":18555,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T05:29:34.000Z","msg":"細個8,90年代親朋戚友都住公屋<br />\n個年代都係正常local港人， 係未有能力買樓<br />\n衛生， 治安真係唔係問題， 打開閘門都無人打劫， 走廊打牌踢波樂也融融<br />\n<br />\n之後慢慢儲到錢都搬走哂， 我識嘅人得返獨居老人仲住公屋<br />\n<br />\n取而代之全部都係蝗同蝻， 一係因為經濟有問題(殘障， 精神病)<br />\n<br />\n根本住過公屋搬走的話， 唔會再想返去公屋住， 梗加唔會買"},{"pid":"ea3a6b15b07a1efcfcc1e11fc8bb53957b947fae","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88a52f1ef6a27b5e968f376e28f2b713ad000f3","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81da67510610cd317a0c9c1942b5606a1f4c352","tid":439652,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個8,90年代親朋戚友都住公屋<br />\n個年代都係正常local港人， 係未有能力買樓<br />\n衛生， 治安真係唔係問題， 打開閘門都無人打劫， 走廊打牌踢波樂也融融<br />\n<br />\n之後慢慢儲到錢都搬走哂， 我識嘅人得返獨居老人仲住公屋<br />\n<br />\n取而代之全部都係蝗同蝻， 一係因為經濟有問題(殘障， 精神病)<br />\n<br />\n根本住過公屋搬走的話， 唔會再想返去公屋住， 梗加唔會買</blockquote><br />\n租置計劃大把人買，買完等三年賣又好，(補地價)租出去又好，都有賺。"},{"pid":"e2cb53486240dc32d0457d0773d819e3a19f807f","tid":439652,"uid":146917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"有分別<br />\n我唔想同班精神病嘅人住"},{"pid":"0854511c34d20a9d78391a08458bee2ab5be7c0a","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cdb837f07f71ca76bc1e3bba802b162c326ed3","tid":439652,"uid":125237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T12:14:54.000Z","msg":"你估屯門好平?"},{"pid":"29de0836081b0ebb9c65da3d358eb3a0c54b9b33","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T01:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6e827dbaa580b1b4d8b1507d8631e712dcb503","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你估屯門好平?</blockquote><br />\n當然<br />\n<br />\n176萬買到449呎香港樓咁抵？！我都想買啊！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/440553/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/440553/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"adc51dd2301e75ee68f9154f96bfa16b7a0d91e6","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f9720d9ec52acaa61c049fea57ea1fca24f48c","tid":439652,"uid":77143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 班中學生連登仔學人係度嫌三嫌四<br />\n人地買綠置居起碼係用自己錢同運氣得翻黎，自己嘅資產<br />\n你班中學中學生食老母住老豆學人嫌綠置居居住環境廢？"},{"pid":"697650f663d3dc923bb12f004df8cb2829ca9e06","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e4752c21dae35f95e1e42fe08b7d0757512cbf","tid":439652,"uid":74259,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T07:22:30.000Z","msg":"成日講鄰居 其實關春事咩 平時鎖埋門跟本冇分別 鄰居最煩就一定係裝修 但係又唔關公屋私樓事 同埋唔好成日ff公屋就係痴線佬集散地啦 香港冇咁多痴線 再講計休憩用地都係公屋多過私樓 係大堂冇咁靚同冇會所會真係影響到生活"},{"pid":"9af5d8de3f4699887cf651a149cf4d6a8a6be6e0","tid":439652,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日講鄰居 其實關春事咩 平時鎖埋門跟本冇分別 鄰居最煩就一定係裝修 但係又唔關公屋私樓事 同埋唔好成日ff公屋就係痴線佬集散地啦 香港冇咁多痴線 再講計休憩用地都係公屋多過私樓 係大堂冇咁靚同冇會所會真係影響到生活</blockquote><br />\n我以前住公屋<br />\n附近有幾個精神病人/綜援家庭<br />\n日日亂拍門叫囂<br />\n夜少少返屋企都驚比人打劫<br />\n(唔好話唐樓舊樓一樣有呢啲問題<br />\n講緊一般屋苑式管理私樓<br />\n已經未計獨立屋半山區嗰啲)"},{"pid":"215668f2e10ec3093ea628eba5a45d7059eaa01e","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff1b65892a072305a3728cff4e6793c51e932d9","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T04:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ab3279d878efc7c65f9dc28a9ea02b1b0d42d2","tid":439652,"uid":54432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>居屋實用D, 大間D...<br />\n無club house ...<br />\n管理費都平啲，裝修得好其實同私樓無分別</blockquote><br />\n問心有club house你覺得你使用率會唔會好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5503a657e318c88f72db913e383d0a290b2fc1","tid":439652,"uid":54432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T04:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋住環境唔係單睇室內<br />\n社區 配套 樓宇問題 治安 衛生...<br />\n全部都影響你生活<br />\n如果你單單覺得閂埋門就得<br />\n其他咩都唔關事<br />\n咁不如訓棺材算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港島大把垃圾私樓係公/居屋附近 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c05a9948d1e4218ea9f60fc6a958ba657f0aab8","tid":439652,"uid":45353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"識人住居屋，有鄰居小事磨擦搵刀傷人坐幾個月，講到尾都有一部份公屋昇上黎。"},{"pid":"b1dfa44148a8f261fa4dce86728363d68e9ac8d5","tid":439652,"uid":45353,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你嗰鄰居個個窮人，全座低質哂</blockquote><br />\n大把公屋富戶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有錢同個人品唔沾關係"},{"pid":"5c0b329b1f757be1ee3fef25d1d2cbedb763eade","tid":439652,"uid":143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9470fec52f9c035fde6dbc8820229ec476928afc","tid":439652,"uid":89909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"比你揀，九龍自置公屋(黃大仙)  vs 屯門私樓，你會買邊度？"},{"pid":"d70ce333525643e1786323969b21b1f3515a0183","tid":439652,"uid":119384,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比你揀，九龍自置公屋(黃大仙)  vs 屯門私樓，你會買邊度？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719f6266b06ce622399733b7d86c7ee87e9a6df7","tid":439652,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有分別<br />\n我唔想同班精神病嘅人住</blockquote><br />\n慈雲山公屋唔知點解收咁多道友，成日喺自動電梯口中下中下"},{"pid":"f8e85d332c35645be951323c1d54db1f06ead2d4","tid":439652,"uid":63779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋住環境唔係單睇室內<br />\n社區 配套 樓宇問題 治安 衛生...<br />\n全部都影響你生活<br />\n如果你單單覺得閂埋門就得<br />\n其他咩都唔關事<br />\n咁不如訓棺材算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講社區治安衛生e d只係得港島傳統<br />\n地段同house有資格,其他都係連公<br />\n屋多。"},{"pid":"6e47f503814a08a65347ba0443837482a75e3b67","tid":439652,"uid":126158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比你揀，九龍自置公屋(黃大仙)  vs 屯門私樓，你會買邊度？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁拎黃大仙同屯門黎比又無得咁比既"},{"pid":"e680a6a8dfa83109576f663587a24f310e253e6e","tid":439652,"uid":13645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"公屋大堂一地煙頭<br />\n走廊又尿跡又橙皮<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"75791d0acad13cc03a770dd7f8ab63ad0adee148","tid":439652,"uid":87172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/7TmDAcu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7TmDAcu.jpg&h=bd65159b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f3d603479848034e3a773eb64a129793ef01a6c","tid":439652,"uid":87172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/n531MEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fn531MEQ.jpg&h=2b892235&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63ac0111680096dd3894c8fb7aab33ccceb5d90a","tid":439652,"uid":126736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:39:32.000Z","msg":"公屋仔就係公屋仔<br />\n連諗野都咁uneducated"},{"pid":"3f0a9620629e3e9c13ee8a6bf628c8b7df0003a4","tid":439652,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:43:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af453602a122e7bcf923d48f59f96f104c7e35b2","tid":439652,"uid":89909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比你揀，九龍自置公屋(黃大仙)  vs 屯門私樓，你會買邊度？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁拎黃大仙同屯門黎比又無得咁比既</blockquote><br />\n咁無理由拎屯門公屋同屯門私樓比啦，一定要有好強既誘引先會將公屋同私樓比，黃大仙就係九龍，交通方便，先有力同屯門私樓一戰"},{"pid":"ce7d367ce0fdf6bb1ffde39968ae733d330ff556","tid":439652,"uid":62079,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇得救既思想<br />\n公屋裝修到豪宅咁都係公屋，地址唔會變，鄰居都係公屋人仕，物管都係公屋質素，唔會因為你補完地價，裝修完高級左"},{"pid":"125a130964d508c2c1452ed680465b9c8cddbec6","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d8da0ec76fd54d0436355bce690036784730b8","tid":439652,"uid":42178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:36:40.000Z","msg":"補咗地價嘅公屋都係公屋"},{"pid":"772eb2927ece80090df28136013ee136ff56e016","tid":439652,"uid":872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:49:32.000Z","msg":"認真問華富呢種仲算唔算普通公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7407c626d0442d9c387156fc96b49c6abc4fbb","tid":439652,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真問華富呢種仲算唔算普通公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中轉屋"},{"pid":"21e61bbb90b369520c1cd48f2b55601db5982fa8","tid":439652,"uid":872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真問華富呢種仲算唔算普通公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中轉屋</blockquote><br />\n咁華貴呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d55283dac134c6c070c81c820e5c8d66326638","tid":439652,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-21T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>居屋實用D, 大間D...<br />\n無club house ...<br />\n管理費都平啲，裝修得好其實同私樓無分別</blockquote><br />\n居屋樓底好低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這個確是！<br />\n壓迫感大！"},{"pid":"715a4b96c4bc7c8b75ce6917c18d049a5fa796bd","tid":439652,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T23:57:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/444643/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/444643/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"4d0ee5b3b5696409b1a1ebb5eca7d4dd3e027106","tid":439652,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:12:18.000Z","msg":"私樓人留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bed8deae6c7310314c539255c3e463794be1f8b1","tid":439652,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:19:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8941bf5d1ade6e91a55a2da37641af1c8df9e994","tid":439652,"uid":51598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇得救既思想<br />\n公屋裝修到豪宅咁都係公屋，地址唔會變，鄰居都係公屋人仕，物管都係公屋質素，唔會因為你補完地價，裝修完高級左</blockquote><br />\n其實係講得幾岩<br />\n公屋三日唔埋就有人跳樓, 火足, 自殺, 嘈交, 打仔, 痴線佬大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我住左私樓20年淨係試過隔離個棟有人跳樓<br />\n最煩最騷擾就係樓上又裝修，隔離個小朋友練琴練樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係講緊想生小朋友既一定住私樓好過公屋<br />\n私樓班小朋友2 3歲就識講英文, 又有禮貌<br />\n相反公屋個班9成9都係老豆係廢中，係大陸娶老婆，生埋d成口蝗語，個樣勁大陸味既小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bdc57edf9634b6dd01391b98590a21aad4fb40","tid":439652,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住秀某坪500呎樓同住跑馬地500呎樓有咩分別？<br />\n肯比錢裝修屋裏面可能真是無分別。<br />\n<br />\n一出門口見到D鄰居，成個區的環境，D人的質素已經一個天一個地！<br />\n響自己居住環境見唔到痴線佬無蝗無南亞人，果一區已經好值錢！</blockquote><br />\n私樓多數見鬼佬，菲傭，印度人家庭多<br />\n未見過蝻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7cbf0a308b5b6fdf5642d56cc823ed3c775469","tid":439652,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:36:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e742337e79a80203254456d233a16a9c5ab3e1f3","tid":439652,"uid":13976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:51:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇得救既思想<br />\n公屋裝修到豪宅咁都係公屋，地址唔會變，鄰居都係公屋人仕，物管都係公屋質素，唔會因為你補完地價，裝修完高級左</blockquote><br />\n其實係講得幾岩<br />\n公屋三日唔埋就有人跳樓, 火足, 自殺, 嘈交, 打仔, 痴線佬大叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我住左私樓20年淨係試過隔離個棟有人跳樓<br />\n最煩最騷擾就係樓上又裝修，隔離個小朋友練琴練樂器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係講緊想生小朋友既一定住私樓好過公屋<br />\n私樓班小朋友2 3歲就識講英文, 又有禮貌<br />\n相反公屋個班9成9都係老豆係廢中，係大陸娶老婆，生埋d成口蝗語，個樣勁大陸味既小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個真，自己住公屋戈邊附近D人都幾好幾nice,但始終樓下公眾位D人鳩下鳩下。你話住私樓D大陸人質素都仲好，公屋戈D真係狗也不屌。<br />\n<br />\n如果計劃生下一代，為下代著想都係住返私樓"},{"pid":"1e60d32efc9989660cff1518faec06831774065c","tid":439652,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:11:49.000Z","msg":"樓主啲思想同比幾千買廉航個呀叔無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d98bdd0d78ba567f32bf7d82c4f2130ff40fc3e","tid":439652,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋住環境唔係單睇室內<br />\n社區 配套 樓宇問題 治安 衛生...<br />\n全部都影響你生活<br />\n如果你單單覺得閂埋門就得<br />\n其他咩都唔關事<br />\n咁不如訓棺材算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c11c49c58cc8b950d8dbb8dad30b54ba9db52da","tid":439652,"uid":154353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:33:01.000Z","msg":"窮撚大西北私樓留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331ed0ba5f12ff70b23731beafc5fbdd0d903a80","tid":439652,"uid":89909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:44:33.000Z","msg":"我份人唔鐘意塞車係度等，如果要住屯門天水圍元朗私樓，我都係情願住番九龍地鐵站隔離果d公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95eaf40124c3dc02e6505dffdf33b2567db7c8e7","tid":439652,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T08:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我份人唔鐘意塞車係度等，如果要住屯門天水圍元朗私樓，我都係情願住番九龍地鐵站隔離果d公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁天水圍私樓又真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本成個區都係for公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ba451331a1b9c18dacc0f9c3627d83f3dea23f","tid":439652,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182e7f82701909979c35f296b057aae7c91456b3","tid":439652,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb5d0ce8735d7fa20c9dabc3a2ceb3a0af0f772","tid":439652,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T15:36:22.000Z","msg":"山頂十萬蚊呎，深水埗唐樓8千蚊呎，點解要俾10萬？<br />\n有d野係窮人唔會明，你覺得一樣咪一樣。"},{"pid":"683e522d2e22113d108e1b4f489a52ab47c546f6","tid":439652,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,